Package: ungeviz
Type: Package
Title: Tools for visualizing uncertainty with ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Claus O.", "Wilke", , "wilke@austin.utexas.edu", c("cre", "aut")))
Description: This package provides add-on functionality for ggplot2 to make
    it easier to visualize uncertainty (which is called Ungewissheit in German).
URL: https://github.com/clauswilke/ungeviz
